  "text": "Spaceflight mutagenesis has been shown to be more efficient than other mutation methods for microbes. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] The unique environments in the outer space, such as microgravity, strong radiation, the presence of high-energy particles, and alternating magnetic fields, can induce gene mutations. [CITATION_4] In this study, the spaceflight mutagenesis technology was used to obtain more mutants.",
